    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Life is one of the greatest mysteries of the universe. From the simplest microbes to complex human beings, life manifests in countless forms, evolving and adapting to its environment. But what exactly is life? How did it come into existence? How does it sustain itself, and what leads to its deterioration? Can life be revived once it has ended? Moreover, how does intelligence emerge, develop, and evolve over time?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
